1 Added GRUB Background

For Existing Triaxis Users

Open terminal Then sudo nano /etc/default/grub
The Uncomment # On GRUB_BACKGROUND"/path/to/wallpaper"
Then Change GRUB_BACKGROUND"/path/to/wallpaper" To GRUB_BACKGROUND"/usr/share/wallpapers/Frozenworld Or Frozenworld Compile IT"
Example GRUB_BACKGROUND"GRUB_BACKGROUND"/usr/share/wallpapers/Frozenworld-Compile-It/Frozenworld (Compile It).png"

